-- China Banks Have `Huge' Fundraising Needs in Next Few Years, Huijin Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-06T07:44:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-06/china-banks-have-huge-fundraising-needs-in-next-few-years-huijin-says.html
China’s biggest banks have “huge”
fundraising needs in the next couple of years as the economy
grows and deposits expand, Li Jiange, vice chairman of Central
Huijin Investment Co., said at a Beijing forum.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
